title: Newly created team looking for top laner, Plat 5+
body:
Semi casual/ambitious team looking for a top laner.
Plat 5+
preferably older than 16.
fluent in English.

We are playing ranked 5s in a quite competitive manner but we are still trying to emphasize fun.
Thus its quite laid back and flexible in terms of practice/schedule.
If you want to have fun and play competitively, hit us up.

IGN: Strikez
